project_descr: The project will address the priority needs in the ministerially endorsed Strategic Plan (SAP) through implementation of the SAP and national Integrated Water Resources Management Plans to strengthen and harmonize ground and surface water management.

outputs.output_descr: Advancing IWRM across the Kura river basin through implementation of the transboundary agreed actions and national plans.

project_title: kura ii: advancing iwrm across the kura river basin
